            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1674037621863-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1674037621863-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cabbage & carrot slaw mix</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong>, mix it all together and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cabbage & carrot slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
