        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>gram flour </strong>and <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>in a bowl with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Add 75ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and whisk everything together until there are no lumps – this is your <strong>batter</strong></p>",
